{% comment %} Bespoke content for the Ultima Luxury Mattress product — layer diagram, comfort
   scale, feature cards, comparison table, testimonial, size guide, FAQ. Ported verbatim
   from ultima.html. Rendered by sections/main-product.liquid via two parts: 'spec' (inside
   the buy panel) and 'body' (the "Inside the Ultima" section onward). {% endcomment %}

{% case part %}

{% when 'spec' %}
    <div class="spec-mini">
        <div><b>Thickness</b>7"</div>
        <div><b>Comfort Scale</b>Medium</div>
        <div><b>Best for</b>Back &amp; combination sleepers</div>
    </div>

{% when 'body' %}
    <section class="story section--dark">
        <blockquote>Obsessed with mattresses, <em>so you can be obsessed with sleep.</em></blockquote>
        <p>Every Ultima Luxury fuses traditional craftsmanship with innovative foam technology — certified foams, precision quilting, and a layer stack we've refined year after year, backed by a 25-year warranty.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="inside">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal" style="margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;max-width:620px;margin-left:0;">
                <h2>Seven layers of performance-driven comfort</h2>
                <p>Tap a layer to see what it does. The Luxury adds Memorest and Cosmic Byte foams to the Ultima stack — a deeper, pressure-melting comfort zone above the same trusted Zero G Latex support core.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="layers-grid">
                <svg class="layer-svg" viewBox="0 0 520 424" role="img" aria-label="Cross-section of the Ultima Luxury mattress showing seven layers">
                    <g id="slabA" class="slab" data-layer="A">
                        <path d="M30 44 Q30 22 66 22 L454 22 Q490 22 490 44 L490 58 L30 58 Z" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M56 36 q13 -6 26 0 M102 36 q13 -6 26 0 M148 36 q13 -6 26 0 M194 36 q13 -6 26 0 M240 36 q13 -6 26 0 M286 36 q13 -6 26 0 M332 36 q13 -6 26 0 M378 36 q13 -6 26 0 M424 36 q13 -6 26 0" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
                        <text x="12" y="46">A</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabB" class="slab" data-layer="B">
                        <rect x="30" y="62" width="460" height="40" fill="#E4F2C5" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M50 82 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
                        <text x="12" y="88">B</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabC" class="slab" data-layer="C">
                        <rect x="30" y="106" width="460" height="46" fill="#E4F2C5" stroke="#3F5E12" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <text x="12" y="135">C</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabD" class="slab" data-layer="D">
                        <rect x="30" y="156" width="460" height="46" fill="#F2F4EC" stroke="#3F5E12" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <text x="12" y="185">D</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabE" class="slab" data-layer="E">
                        <rect x="30" y="206" width="460" height="50" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#9D9E9E" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <g stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none" opacity=".6">
                            <circle cx="80" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="150" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="220" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="290" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="360" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="430" cy="231" r="9"/>
                        </g>
                        <text x="12" y="237">E</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabF" class="slab" data-layer="F">
                        <rect x="30" y="260" width="460" height="76" fill="#3F5E12" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <g stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" opacity=".8">
                            <path d="M70 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M140 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M210 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M280 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M350 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M420 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26"/>
                        </g>
                        <text x="12" y="304" fill="#FEFEFE">F</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabG" class="slab" data-layer="G">
                        <path d="M30 340 L490 340 L490 364 Q490 388 450 388 L70 388 Q30 388 30 364 Z" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M60 366 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.1" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
                        <text x="12" y="370">G</text>
                    </g>
                </svg>

                <div id="layerList">
                    <div class="layer-item active" data-layer="A" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">A.</span> Luxnit Premium Fabric</h3>
                        <p>Premium stretch-knit fabric offering breathability, durability, and a refined soft touch.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="B" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">B.</span> Aeroflex Quilting</h3>
                        <p>Breathable quilted comfort layer offering enhanced softness and airflow.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="C" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">C.</span> Memorest Foam</h3>
                        <p>Body-contouring memory foam that reduces pressure points — the Luxury-exclusive upgrade.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="D" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">D.</span> Cosmic Byte Foam</h3>
                        <p>Balanced comfort layer with responsive support that deepens the comfort zone.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="E" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">E.</span> Cloud Sense Foam</h3>
                        <p>Plush, adaptive layer for a cloud-like feel that cushions every pressure point.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="F" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">F.</span> Zero G Latex Foam</h3>
                        <p>Firm, supportive latex core delivering orthopedic support and superior durability.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="G" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">G.</span> Soft Foam Quilting</h3>
                        <p>Cushioned quilting at the base for additional softness and pressure relief.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="firmness">
                <h3>Where the Ultima Luxury sits on our comfort scale</h3>
                <div class="scale"><div class="scale-marker" style="left:54%;" title="Medium"></div></div>
                <div class="scale-labels"><span>Ultra plush</span><b>Ultima Luxury — medium</b><span>Extra firm</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--paper">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal">
                <h2>Durability with comfort — by design</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-cards">
                <article class="fcard reveal" style="transition-delay:0ms;">
                    <div class="fcard-media"><img src="{{ 'product-ultima-angle4.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Close-up of the Ultima's Luxnit fabric and tufting" loading="lazy"></div>
                    <div class="fcard-body">
                        <h3>Luxnit Breathability</h3>
                        <p>A precision-tufted stretch-knit cover that circulates air all night — made for Indian summers, not against them.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="fcard reveal" style="transition-delay:80ms;">
                    <div class="fcard-media"><img src="{{ 'product-ultima-angle2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Side profile of the Ultima Luxury showing its layered construction" loading="lazy"></div>
                    <div class="fcard-body">
                        <h3>Zero G Latex Support</h3>
                        <p>A firm, high-density latex core beneath the plush layers keeps your spine aligned in every sleeping position.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="fcard reveal" style="transition-delay:160ms;">
                    <div class="fcard-media"><img src="{{ 'product-ultima-angle3.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Front view of the Ultima Luxury mattress with plush pillow top" loading="lazy"></div>
                    <div class="fcard-body">
                        <h3>Triple Comfort Zone</h3>
                        <p>Memorest, Cosmic Byte, and Cloud Sense foams stack into the deepest comfort zone of any Ultima — performance and plushness in one.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="compare">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal">
                <h2>Which Ultima is yours?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="table-scroll">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr><th>Feature</th><th>Classic</th><th>Premium</th><th class="hl">Luxury</th></tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><th>Top Fabric</th><td>Super Plush Luxeknit Fabric</td><td>Super Plush Luxeknit Fabric</td><td class="hl">Luxnit Premium Fabric</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Comfort Layer</th><td>Aeroflex Foam Quilting</td><td>Aeroflex Foam Quilting</td><td class="hl">Aeroflex Quilting</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Body Support Layer</th><td>Cloud Sense Foam</td><td>Cosmic Byte Foam + Cloud Sense Foam</td><td class="hl">Memorest Foam + Cosmic Byte Foam + Cloud Sense Foam</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Main Support</th><td>Zero G Latex Foam</td><td>Zero G Latex Foam</td><td class="hl">Zero G Latex Foam</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Bottom Layer</th><td>Soft Foam with Quilting</td><td>Soft Foam with Quilting</td><td class="hl">Soft Foam Quilting</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Thickness</th><td>6"</td><td>6.5"</td><td class="hl">7"</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Comfort Scale</th><td>Firm</td><td>Medium Firm</td><td class="hl">Medium</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Warranty</th><td>25 Years + 5 Years Full Replacement*</td><td>25 Years + 5 Years Full Replacement*</td><td class="hl">25 Years + 5 Years Full Replacement*</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p class="compare-note">*As per Foamico warranty terms. Not sure which one to pick? <a href="{{ pages.mattresses.url | default: '/pages/mattresses' }}#compare">Use our comparison tool</a> or visit our store to try them in person.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--paper">
        <div class="wrap" style="text-align:center;">
            <span class="stars reveal" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
            <div class="quote-banner reveal" style="margin-top:16px;">
                <blockquote>"I wanted something firm enough for my back but not stiff — the Ultima Luxury nailed it. Three years in, it still feels as supportive as day one, and that 25-year warranty is real peace of mind."</blockquote>
                <cite>— Verified buyer, Gurugram</cite>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    {% render 'size-guide', product: product %}

    <section class="section section--paper" id="faq">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal">
                <h2>Mattress FAQs</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What makes the Luxury different from the Classic and Premium?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>All three share the Zero G Latex support core and Aeroflex quilting. The Luxury adds two extra comfort foams — Memorest and Cosmic Byte — above the Cloud Sense layer, creating the deepest, most pressure-relieving comfort zone in the Ultima range.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Is the Ultima Luxury too firm for side sleepers?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>No — the Medium comfort scale and three comfort foams up top cushion the shoulders and hips, while the Zero G Latex core underneath keeps the spine aligned regardless of sleep position.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Will it sleep hot?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>The Luxnit stretch fabric and quilted comfort layers are chosen for breathability, so air keeps moving through the sleep surface all night.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What does the warranty cover?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Every Ultima comes with a 25-year warranty, including 5 years of full replacement*, covering manufacturing defects under normal use. Full terms are available from our team.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Can I try it before buying?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — visit our store in Ghitorni, New Delhi to try the full Ultima range in person, or call us at +91 74969 82886 (Mon–Sat, 9 AM–6 PM) and our sleep experts will help you choose.</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

{% endcase %}
